# Drop your logo PNG/JPG files here.
# Marquee.tsx auto-discovers them via import.meta.glob — no code changes needed.
#
# Supported formats: .png .jpg .jpeg .webp .svg (any case)
# Filenames with spaces and Arabic characters work correctly.
# Vite URL-encodes them internally at build time.
#
# Expected files (from brief):
#   tataaaaa.png         zaytona.png           chickien fire.png
#   ASMAK.png            chickien wings.png    ELBOKHARY.png
#   Crazy burger.png     عزوز.png              qasr elmandy.png
#   power burger.png     BIG BELLY.png         flat.png
#   61.png               valancia.png          taag.png
#   sokr w labn.png      the burgrest.jpg      mad shrimp.png
#   wings and shrimp.png dallah.png            ALADIEN.png
#   wild burger.png      feat2eat.png          mr koko.png
#   marhaba.png
#
# Until files are added, the site shows the Lovable CDN fallback logos.
